{"id":426396,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/01/【麻辣总局】-5/","date":"2016-01-23T07:51:17Z","modified":"2016-02-11T22:09:24Z","title":"【一颗腮挺】邝飚：赵氏春晚","content":"<p>作者：邝飚</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/mmexport1453532849130.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-426397\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/mmexport1453532849130.jpg\" alt=\"mmexport1453532849130\" width=\"475\" height=\"\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong><em>事件背景：</em></strong></p>\n<p>央视近日公布了2016年春晚吉祥物“康康”3D形象：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/401276061349430120472AF7BFAE458D.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-426402\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/401276061349430120472AF7BFAE458D.jpg\" alt=\"401276061349430120472AF7BFAE458D\" width=\"450\" height=\"\" /></a></p>\n<p>然而原作者韩美林的原稿是这样的：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/765E8E404A7C1BD261E098FA50807611.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-426403\"><img  src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/765E8E404A7C1BD261E098FA50807611.jpg\" alt=\"765E8E404A7C1BD261E098FA50807611\" width=\"450\" height=\"\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/d1046db2jw1f07ab4793xj214w0rsgrn.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-426401\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/d1046db2jw1f07ab4793xj214w0rsgrn.jpg\" alt=\"d1046db2jw1f07ab4793xj214w0rsgrn\" width=\"450\" height=\"\" /></a></p>\n<p>猴年春晚吉祥物被网民戏称为“猴腮雷”，引来一波恶搞风潮（以下图片来自新浪微博）：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/7fd54a81jw1f0851xi0elj20c81i30wx-copy.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-426399\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/7fd54a81jw1f0851xi0elj20c81i30wx-copy.jpg\" alt=\"7fd54a81jw1f0851xi0elj20c81i30wx copy\" width=\"400\" height=\"\" /></a><br />\n<span style=\"color: #808080;\">作者：新浪微博 <a style=\"color: #808080;\" href=\"http://weibo.com/lastangel17th\">@使徒子</a></span></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/756f9a33jw1f07hs4ari0j208r08iabz.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-426398\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/756f9a33jw1f07hs4ari0j208r08iabz.jpg\" alt=\"756f9a33jw1f07hs4ari0j208r08iabz\" width=\"315\" height=\"306\" /></a><br />\n<span style=\"color: #808080;\">作者：新浪微博 </span><a href=\"http://weibo.com/1970248243/DecEiFet1\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">@o西歪歪o</span> </a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/0066Ifwvjw1f08lyppzy0j30b30qu752.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-426404\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/0066Ifwvjw1f08lyppzy0j30b30qu752.jpg\" alt=\"0066Ifwvjw1f08lyppzy0j30b30qu752\" width=\"399\" height=\"966\" /></a><br />\n<span style=\"color: #808080;\">作者不详</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/59fc3998gw1f07k2iwu5ij20c82kbq5r.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-426405\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/59fc3998gw1f07k2iwu5ij20c82kbq5r.jpg\" alt=\"59fc3998gw1f07k2iwu5ij20c82kbq5r\" width=\"400\" height=\"\" /></a><br />\n<span style=\"color: #808080;\"><a style=\"color: #808080;\" href=\"http://weibo.com/lastangel17th\">@使徒子</a>原作</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/59fc3998gw1f07k2j17i2j20c81zpafr.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-426406\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/59fc3998gw1f07k2j17i2j20c81zpafr.jpg\" alt=\"59fc3998gw1f07k2j17i2j20c81zpafr\" width=\"400\" height=\"2346\" /></a><br />\n<span style=\"color: #808080;\"><a style=\"color: #808080;\" href=\"http://weibo.com/1509702040/Dedai1K9m\">@雨声敲敲</a>的后续</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/7dced06cgw1f07hx3yxzej20sf1zq46i.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-426407\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/7dced06cgw1f07hx3yxzej20sf